%F A007900 G.f.: (1+54*x^2+20*x+20*x^3+x^4)/(1-x)^4 = 1+24*x*(x+1)^2/(x-1)^4.
%F A007900 G.f. for coordination sequence of D_n lattice: (Sum(binomial(2*n, 2*i)*z^i, i=0..n)-2*n*z*(1+z)^(n-2))/(1-z)^n.
%p A007900 if n=0 then 1 else 8*n*(2*n^2+1); fi;
%t A007900 A007900[n_] := If[n == 0, 1, 8*n*(2*n^2 + 1)]; Array[A007900, 50, 0] (* _Paolo Xausa_, May 20 2026 *)
